  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Easy Park Plus画一个客户账户的生命周期状态图。起点是用户在Wiki页面注册，然后进入Registered状态，验证邮箱后变成Active。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Registered",
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Registered到Active的触发条件是邮箱或身份验证通过。那Active之后有哪些分支？比如账户会不会被暂停或注销？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Active有两个出口：一个是违反政策或付款出问题，进入Suspended状态；另一个是用户自己申请或管理员操作，进入Deactivated。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Suspended",
        "Deactivated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：WikiPage到Registered，验证后到Active，然后分岔到Suspended和Deactivated。Suspended这边需要能回到Active吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended",
        "Deactivated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，Suspended问题解决后可以恢复Active。另外Suspended也能直接Deactivated，和Active那边一样的触发条件。最后Deactivated要进到SprintBacklog做归档处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended",
        "Active",
        "Deactivated",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Suspended到Active是问题解决，Suspended到Deactivated是用户或管理员操作，Deactivated终点是SprintBacklog。Suspended状态需要加注释说明限制访问吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended",
        "Active",
        "Deactivated",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，在Suspended右边加个注释，写\"账户访问受限\"。标题用Easy Park Plus - Customer Account State Diagram，标注一下Groupware_KanbanBoard。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended",
        "note",
        "title",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了，整个流程从WikiPage注册开始，经过验证激活，支持暂停恢复和最终注销归档，Suspended状态带访问限制说明。",
